<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Belief_perseverance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>Anderson, C. A. (2007). Belief perseverance. (pp.&#160;109–110). In R. F. Baumeister &amp; K. D. Vohs (Eds.), <i>Encyclopedia of Social Psychology.</i> Thousand Oaks, CA: Sage.
